  <h2>
    <span>喜欢读&#34;恶意&#34;的人也喜欢</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


  <div class="content clearfix">
      
      <dl class="">
        <dt>
            <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3211779/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '3211779', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})"><img class="m_sub_img" src="https://img9.doubanio.com/view/subject/s/public/s3254244.jpg"/></a>
        </dt>
        <dd>
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3211779/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '3211779', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})" class="">
            嫌疑人X的献身
          </a>
          <span class="subject-rate">8.9</span>
        </dd>
      </dl>
      
